ime":"2019-07-25T00:05:23.000Z","msg":"扭扭擰擰<br />\n<br />\n講就話唔畀你屌<br />\n下次咪又係腿張開"},{"pid":"7b0f5648172d4a9127658d8436fbb021643acb8f","tid":1362262,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:06:59.000Z","msg":"國徽係底線, 就出解放軍, 上左外國報紙, <br />\n同係歷史書, 怕唔怕俾人笑"},{"pid":"4301e5a9c5272d90fe3ad4823a44eb23d644d7ea","tid":1362262,"uid":71583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:08:51.000Z","msg":"襯未真係出解放軍之前，呼籲攞晒銀行啲錢出嚟換定美元現金、金條，或者帶得走嘅有形資產<br />\n<br />\n到時股市大跌、銀行冇錢拎，唔好話中國冇提過大家撤資<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bded8f2651ba0f3e2906e61cab0bd1ac681db31","tid":1362262,"uid":16372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:19:02.000Z","msg":"市民要求出解放軍"},{"pid":"69af6e64f397d2326d752a10bbfd506b1465524c","tid":1362262,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bded8f2651ba0f3e2906e61cab0bd1ac681db31","tid":1362262,"uid":16372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:19:02.000Z","msg":"市民要求出解放軍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:21:16.000Z","msg":"去中聯辦請願出兵鎮壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0521206d319b1db11070052f9093ed029358ff75","tid":1362262,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:21:37.000Z","msg":"終於玩到尾任<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac49b751167feaf2190bbe922421c7b3cf40f87","tid":1362262,"uid":191968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:57:54.000Z","msg":"你地係咪真係支持我要攬炒巴架<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359103</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f6db757ba6e814fdb273d970000f5b6a383acc92","tid":1362262,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:01:34.000Z","msg":"推到你地出解放軍"},{"pid":"b70de75c09e755198ce28005ccadd0678c76d38d","tid":1362262,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:04:43.000Z","msg":"連登仔強烈要求中共政府立即出動解放軍暴力鎮壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n共軍來了我回家<br />\n齊齊攬炒笑哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec498c0eecbb344daf6c0491c962283ea46bcbc6","tid":1362262,"uid":288670,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:11:32.000Z","msg":"中共依家都講到話有下次再搞中聯辦就出解放軍 不如直接幫幫中共"},{"pid":"16af2b02fe2050a7f2d162fd446551f0f56b120a","tid":1362262,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:12:53.000Z","msg":"民不畏死 奈何以死懼之"},{"pid":"8834051e68930a9d4c890ff886e1dd4039f4150e","tid":1362262,"uid":77905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:14:22.000Z","msg":"褲都除埋而家話唔洗出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d1bcd9d9e8104be8662af57669b867c3aaf4c5","tid":1362262,"uid":57329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"請求馬上出動解放軍<br />\n殲滅勾結黑幫嘅警察部雙方<br />\n幫助香港市民對付兩大邪惡勢力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0700d7067879ea5aaacf187040c70b5163edc3e0","tid":1362262,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:38:17.000Z","msg":"無香港:<br />\n<br />\n有你班仆街換美金?<br />\n保障財產唔被國內鬥爭影響? <br />\n有安全飲食, 醫療? <br />\n比你係香港讀大學受高等教育?<br />\n<br />\n你咪出兵, 我就想睇下中國唯一既出氣口無埋你既國運會點亨昌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1989年12月，中共前總書記江澤民接見英國特使柯利達時，再向港人派定心丸，「有的香港人不大理解，說『井水不犯河水，河水必定犯井水』。其實，我這句話完整地說是『井水不犯河水，河水不犯井水』」。<br />\n<br />\n河水不犯井水，不等於不干預港事務。國務院前副總理錢其琛於1996年出席一個座談會時，再闡釋鄧小平一國兩制概念，「國家主體實行社會主義，香港實行資本主義，是井水不犯河水，河水不犯井水」。<br />\n<br />\n由過渡期到今天回歸20年，河水有否侵犯井水，<span style=\"color: orange;\">就任由中方怎去演繹。</span>回歸後居港權事件觸發人大首次釋法，北京指沒干預香港司法獨立。2010年，港區人大關注內地毒奶粉受害兒童家長趙連海的案件，港澳辦主任王光亞便高調告誡港人，「井水不犯河水」，強調外人不應干預內地司法獨立。</span>"},{"pid":"11f2842c11ea80e1337826db4fd596c85fef6365","tid":1362262,"uid":18587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:40:28.000Z","msg":"有無統計最近講左幾多次？"},{"pid":"c63cdd987212a8958b4570afa0cb415a1923c290","tid":1362262,"uid":125680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a35900555b99cbe71017cddf527fd07d7bd9273d","tid":1362262,"uid":253016,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"98389b4e7fdc7a669309e5c97bce7534ce3f03b3","tid":1362262,"uid":125680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91efed80889bfaace510c955ee73e4c4ef9d1650","tid":1362262,"uid":253016,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T23:29:29.000Z","msg":"倘<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再</span></span>出現侮辱國家事件<br />\n<br />\n佢地話再搞中聯辦就出解放軍黎香港<br />\n好撚怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果佢地講左又唔算數咁點算</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T23:30:35.000Z","msg":"未慣？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T23:32:23.000Z","msg":"咁都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唯有侮辱多幾次睇下有冇轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:34:18.000Z","msg":"好暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56841f0781f103145afcf670e9d2bc55415ae498","tid":1362262,"uid":33060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:35:02.000Z","msg":"幾撚時出呀？<br />\n快撚d啦 你收埋香港皮 我睇你點樣有咁多錢去打貿易戰"},{"pid":"d5bb713be6ebee9e299326fd3adf423159dfa952","tid":1362262,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:44:28.00